Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.31,0:42:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,应该看看其他人质有没有谁想达成协议的\N{\rEN}if any of the other hostages want to cut a deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.10,0:42:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这可能是我们的丰收时刻\N{\rEN}This could be a bumper time for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.43,0:42:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 这感觉不太好\N{\rEN}Well, this doesn't feel great.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.76,0:42:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 软技能 女性责任的狗屎工作\N{\rEN}No. No, soft skills, lady-duty shit-work.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.47,0:42:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,一点也不好\N{\rEN}Not great at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.47,0:42:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,参议员 当我读到我的游轮部门\N{\rEN}Senators, when I read of the abuses of power
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.39,0:42:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,涉嫌滥用职权时...\N{\rEN}alleged in my cruise division...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.22,0:42:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧...那是我一生中最糟糕的一天\N{\rEN}well... that was the worst day of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.01,0:42:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我想到 坏事可能在我不知情的情况下\N{\rEN}To think bad things might have gone on
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.43,0:42:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,继续发生\N{\rEN}without my knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.68,0:43:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,坦白说...\N{\rEN}And frankly...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.72,0:43:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道我是否会原谅自己\N{\rEN}I don't know if I'll ever forgive myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.76,0:43:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我们将进行调查 我们会确保\N{\rEN}But we will investigate, and we will make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.22,0:43:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,每一个受害者都得到补偿 每一个不法行为...\N{\rEN}every victim is compensated, and every act of wrongdoing...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.72,0:43:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,都受到法律的严惩\N{\rEN}punished to the full extent of the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.56,0:43:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是希望 上帝保佑 你们相信我的话\N{\rEN}I just hope, so help me God, you believe me when I say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.76,0:43:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢\N{\rEN}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.72,0:43:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,操 说得好\N{\rEN}Fuck, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.68,0:43:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,伊维斯参议员 下面由你发言\N{\rEN}Senator Eavis? Time is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.10,0:43:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 主席女士\N{\rEN}Thank you, Madam Chairwoman.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.89,0:43:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,爱默生说过 "每一个机构都是一个人的缩影 "\N{\rEN}Emerson said, "Every institution is the shadow of a single man."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.51,0:43:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,在韦斯达 那个人就是洛根·罗伊 不是吗\N{\rEN}At Waystar, that man is Logan Roy, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.72,0:43:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我...\N{\rEN}Well, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.26,0:43:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然不会和爱默生先生争论\N{\rEN}I'm certainly not gonna argue with Mr. Emerson.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.72,0:43:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你的游轮是为了牟利 你的新闻也是为了牟利\N{\rEN}Your cruises run for profit, your news runs for profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.01,0:43:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,把新闻当做你个人的提款机\N{\rEN}Is that any way to keep the life blood
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.10,0:43:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这是让民主的血液\N{\rEN}of a democracy going,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.68,0:44:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,继续流动的方法吗\N{\rEN}by using news as your own personal ATM?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.43,0:44:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,呃...我...我可以发言吗\N{\rEN}Uh... If-- If I may.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.10,0:44:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯...我想你可能有点误解 参议员\N{\rEN}Um... I think you might be under a misapprehension, Senator.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.35,0:44:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,在这个国家 所有的新闻媒体\N{\rEN}In this country, all news,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.43,0:44:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,从时代杂志到超市小报\N{\rEN}from the Times to the supermarket tabloid,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.89,0:44:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,都是为了牟利 先生\N{\rEN}is for profit, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.35,0:44:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没有官方媒体 我很确定你知道这一点\N{\rEN}We don't have a state media. As I'm sure you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.81,0:44:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,要找官媒 你得去中国或者俄罗斯\N{\rEN}you'd have to go to China or Russia for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.10,0:44:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-噢 漂亮 狠扇了吉尔一耳光  -我们还没有官方媒体...\N{\rEN}-Ooh, snap! Snap on Gil! -We don't have a state media yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.56,0:44:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们录下来了吗 卡罗丽娜\N{\rEN}Have we got that, Karolina?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.47,0:44:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们让代理人准备好这句台词\N{\rEN}Let's get the surrogates prepped with that line.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.26,0:44:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他们称吉尔为"疯脑圣人" 因为他很少发表讲话\N{\rEN}They call Gil "Meth-Head Santa" Because he so rarely delivers.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.64,0:44:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我想说的是 在你们的游轮部门\N{\rEN}What I'm getting at, is it any surprise
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.39,0:44:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,剥削和掩盖行为大行其道\N{\rEN}that, uh, exploitation and cover-up runs rife
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.47,0:44:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这有什么稀奇的呢\N{\rEN}at your cruise division?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.85,0:44:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是 剥削\N{\rEN}I mean, exploitation is at
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.01,0:44:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是你们的商业模式的核心\N{\rEN}the heart of your business model.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.18,0:44:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我...我当然会不同意 但是 呃...\N{\rEN}Well, I-- I would, of course, disagree, but, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.35,0:44:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 就过往而言...\N{\rEN}but in terms of the historic...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.14,0:44:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,过往...\N{\rEN}historical...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.81,0:45:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,过往对玩忽职守的指控...\N{\rEN}historic charges of practice-- malpractice, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.47,0:45:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,洛根·罗伊先生 你们的游轮部门保留影子日志\N{\rEN}Mr. Logan Roy, what did you personally know
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.47,0:45:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,以此来混淆不法行为\N{\rEN}about the operation of a system of obfuscation
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.76,0:45:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,对于这样的制度运作\N{\rEN}of wrongdoing in your cruise division...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.68,0:45:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你个人有什么了解吗\N{\rEN}by the means of the keeping of shadow logs?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.26,0:45:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信 那个时候我儿子\N{\rEN}At that point, I believe my son was across
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.56,0:45:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-也在参与运营 对吧  -哪个时候\N{\rEN}-that operation, right? -At which point?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.85,0:45:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他负责娱乐运营的时候\N{\rEN}At the point he was across entertainment operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.85,0:45:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以和他说\N{\rEN}You can talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.10,0:45:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那 肯德尔·罗伊先生\N{\rEN}Mr. Kendall Roy, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.85,0:45:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-告诉我们有关影子日志的事情  -好的 你知道吗\N{\rEN}-Tell us about the shadow logs. -Okay, you know what,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.01,0:45:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 主席女士 我...我可以说一会吗\N{\rEN}I'm sorry, Madam Chairwoman, can-- can I speak for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.97,0:45:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你知道吗 我...我今天真诚地来到这里\N{\rEN}Because you know, I-- I'm here in good faith today,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.18,0:45:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我很愿意和你谈谈 参议员 和委员会\N{\rEN}I'm very willing to talk you, Senator, and this committee
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.47,0:45:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,谈谈我们的运营 但是 我们废话少说吧\N{\rEN}through our operations, but, uh, let's cut the BS,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.89,0:45:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗 因为在我看来 这项调查\N{\rEN}shall we? Because it seems to me that this investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.97,0:45:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 不是关于游轮行业的\N{\rEN}uh, is not about proper oversight
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.72,0:46:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,规范和标准的适当的监督\N{\rEN}of cruise industry codes and standards,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.97,0:46:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,或是某件二十年前的非常令人遗憾\N{\rEN}or some highly regrettable but isolated incidents
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.06,0:46:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但是孤立的事件\N{\rEN}from nearly two decades ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.51,0:46:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这项调查给我的感觉是\N{\rEN}What this feels to me it's about
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.39,0:46:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你个人不喜欢我父亲\N{\rEN}is your personal dislike of my father,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.60,0:46:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你对他的报纸和他的新闻频道\N{\rEN}and your ideological hatred of his newspapers
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.26,0:46:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是 泛美网络的成功故事\N{\rEN}and his news channels, and in particular,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.01,0:46:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,充满了意识形态的仇恨\N{\rEN}of the, uh, success story which is ATN,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.51,0:46:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,然而 在过去四个月里 你在泛美网络\N{\rEN}on which you've appeared, I think, 14 times
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.72,0:46:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我想 应该是出现过14次 参议员\N{\rEN}in the last four months, Senator.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.68,0:46:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好 好 好\N{\rEN}Good, good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.85,0:46:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,伊维斯参议员 在我看来\N{\rEN}Senator Eavis, it seems to me
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.31,0:46:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,既然你在意识形态上不认同我们\N{\rEN}that since you don't agree with us ideologically,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.97,0:46:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们说再多都没用\N{\rEN}that nothing we can say will be enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.56,0:46:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,再卑躬屈膝也不够\N{\rEN}no groveling will be low enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.64,0:46:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,而且尽管你很想指责我们有偏见\N{\rEN}and as much as you like to accuse us of bias,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.81,0:46:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 今天 你才是那个带着偏见的人\N{\rEN}uh, today, you're the one with the bias.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.97,0:46:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 我想说 继续吧 尽你所能打击我们好了\N{\rEN}So, I say go ahead. Hit us as hard as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.56,0:46:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以接受 我们没有什么可隐藏的\N{\rEN}We can take it. We have nothing to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.43,0:46:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那 她在等我们 是吗\N{\rEN}So, she's expecting us, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.10,0:46:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我不会进去的\N{\rEN}Look, I'm not going in.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.72,0:47:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,说真的吗 你要...你要让我独立面对吗\N{\rEN}Seriously? You're... You're leaving it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.81,0:47:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,西沃恩 你也不必这样做\N{\rEN}Siobhan, you don't have to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.39,0:47:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,如果她要去作证 而且引人注目...\N{\rEN}If she speaks and she's compelling...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.18,0:47:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那我家族的公司就完蛋了\N{\rEN}then that's it for my family's company.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.18,0:47:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,所以...是的 我确实必须去\N{\rEN}So... yeah. I do have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.26,0:47:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 瑞亚\N{\rEN}Thanks, Rhea.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.64,0:47:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢你的发言\N{\rEN}Thank you so much for your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.81,0:47:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 罗伯茨先生 我们现在可以悄悄灌输一点\N{\rEN}Ah, Mr. Roberts. We can now slip into something
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.76,0:47:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,一点稍微舒适的内容了\N{\rEN}a little bit more comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.89,0:47:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经感觉好多了\N{\rEN}I already feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.64,0:47:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我想立即说一声 郑重声明 两位……\N{\rEN}And I want to say right off, for the record, gentlemen...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.31,0:47:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢你们\N{\rEN}I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.81,0:47:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我想和你们俩一起喝一杯\N{\rEN}I'd like to have a drink with both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.35,0:47:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我和我妻子曾经一起乘坐过你的其中一条游轮\N{\rEN}And I have taken one of your cruises with my wife
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.10,0:48:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,坦率地说 那是令人愉快的旅程\N{\rEN}and it was, frankly, delightful.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.68,0:48:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 谢谢您 参议员 您真是和气\N{\rEN}Well, thank you, Senator, that's very kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.43,0:48:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 小心\N{\rEN}No, no. Careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.01,0:48:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 你好 我是西沃恩·罗伊 谢谢你见我\N{\rEN}Hi. Hi, Shiv Roy. Thank you for seeing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.85,0:48:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想找个机会来打个招呼\N{\rEN}I just wanted the opportunity to say hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.35,0:48:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我想说 我意识到\N{\rEN}And I want to say I realize
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.01,0:48:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个难以想象的困难情况\N{\rEN}this is an incredibly difficult situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.97,0:48:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我...我希望你知道 我深深地感谢你\N{\rEN}so I-- I want you to know I deeply appreciate you
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.47,0:48:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-花时间  -对 嗯...\N{\rEN}-taking the time. -Right. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.14,0:48:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我不确定我应该...我...我以为这会是一次\N{\rEN}I'm not sure I should-- I-- I thought this was gonna be
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.81,0:48:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,和瑞亚的非常私人的会面\N{\rEN}a very unofficial thing with Rhea?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.35,0:48:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 是的\N{\rEN}Uh-huh. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.51,0:48:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯...这感觉很不一样\N{\rEN}Uh... This feels very different.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.10,0:48:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不 她很忙 嗯...但是她稍后会加入\N{\rEN}No, she's busy. Uh... But she will join later on.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.18,0:48:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-我...  -对我...我...\N{\rEN}-I-- -Right. I j-- I--
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.60,0:48:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是不知道我会不会感到不舒服\N{\rEN}I just don't know if I feel comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.56,0:48:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 但是我不是来这里阻止你去作证的\N{\rEN}Oh, but I'm not here to stop you testifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.51,0:48:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-当然  -嗯 而且我不是来这里给你提任何条件的\N{\rEN}-Sure. -Yeah. And I'm not here to offer you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.22,0:48:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我是来这里倾听 尝试理解你的\N{\rEN}I'm here to listen, and to try to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.39,0:49:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,只是想了解我们做错了什么以及如何补救\N{\rEN}Just trying to understand what we did wrong and how I can fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.10,0:49:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 这个时间出现 想要了解情况...\N{\rEN}Well, it's a very convenient time to show up...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.06,0:49:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-也太巧了吧  -噢...\N{\rEN}-wanting to understand. -Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.64,0:49:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-我觉得你很勇敢  -好的 谢谢\N{\rEN}-I think you're brave. -Well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.97,0:49:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的 不 不 下来不要爬太高\N{\rEN}Honey, no. No, get down. Don't go too high.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.35,0:49:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,过来 过来\N{\rEN}Come here! Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.39,0:49:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 噢 我的天啦 啊\N{\rEN}What? Oh, my God! Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.68,0:49:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来了\N{\rEN}There we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.47,0:49:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 哇 这高跟鞋疼死我了\N{\rEN}Oh, wow. These just kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.93,0:49:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,深有体会 过来...\N{\rEN}I know. Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.93,0:49:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 这样 嗯...\N{\rEN}You know, look, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.22,0:49:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我的...我爸...我爸在几个月前\N{\rEN}My-- My dad... My dad, a couple months ago,
