Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.64,0:49:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,而我会很坦率地和你谈\N{\rEN}And I'm gonna be very frank with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.72,0:49:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不玩任何花招 我不信任他 好吗\N{\rEN}put my cards on the table, I don't trust him. Okay?
