Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.35,0:50:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我想 你知道吗\N{\rEN}Well, I guess, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.81,0:50:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我唯一想问你的问题是...\N{\rEN}the only question I would have for you is just...
