Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.64,0:50:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 终于说到正题了\N{\rEN}Okay, here it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.56,0:51:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不 实话实说 问一个更好的问题\N{\rEN}Nope, honestly? A better question.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.01,0:51:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你真正希望发生的是什么\N{\rEN}What do you actually want to happen?
