Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.51,0:51:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\rEN}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.89,0:51:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 你想坐下吗\N{\rEN}Hey, you want to sit down?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.72,0:51:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是 好事情是\N{\rEN}I mean, the good thing is,
