Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.31,0:56:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我不知道该问什么 你告诉我\N{\rEN}No. I don't know what to ask. You tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.47,0:56:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 这都是...你知道的\N{\rEN}Well, it's all... You know.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.85,0:56:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,很久以前的事了\N{\rEN}It goes a long way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.35,0:56:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你...你以前有没有让编辑\N{\rEN}Did you-- Did you ever have an editor
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.85,0:57:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,用手帮你举着毛衣\N{\rEN}who put a hand up a sweater?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.72,0:57:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那 以前的办事风格不太一样\N{\rEN}Well, things were done differently in those days.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.43,0:57:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能毫不知情地管理公司\N{\rEN}I can't fly blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.01,0:57:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,莱斯特·麦克林托克是你的朋友吗\N{\rEN}Was Lester McClintock a friend of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.14,0:57:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我不认为他是我的朋友 不是\N{\rEN}No, I wouldn't say he was a friend, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.68,0:57:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你曾经告诉我 他是一位密友\N{\rEN}You once told me he was a close friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.39,0:57:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-你告诉我的  -好吧...\N{\rEN}-You told me that. -Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.31,0:57:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友 密友 同事 我也说不清楚\N{\rEN}Friend, close friend, colleague, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.68,0:57:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这算是...一种超能力 对吧\N{\rEN}It's kind of a-- a superpower, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.26,0:57:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,当着别人的面撒谎而若无其事\N{\rEN}If you can lie to someone like that, to their face.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.97,0:57:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是 我知道你在说谎\N{\rEN}I mean, I know you're lying,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.47,0:57:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我还是觉得你说得很合理 而且很吸引人\N{\rEN}but I still find you very plausible and appealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.81,0:57:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我词不达意\N{\rEN}I misspoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.51,0:57:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\rEN}Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.72,0:57:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,原谅我\N{\rEN}Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.22,0:57:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 有些事情就是会时不时地发生\N{\rEN}But there are some things that went on from time to time,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.31,0:57:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,而我只是想保护你\N{\rEN}and I just wanted to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.06,0:57:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-我不需要你的保护  -嗯 你知道吗 作为下一任总裁\N{\rEN}-I don't need your protection. -Well, you know, as the next CEO,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.43,0:57:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,避开某些区域可能比较明智\N{\rEN}it might be wise to keep clean of certain areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.47,0:57:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在想这事\N{\rEN}I've been thinking about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.81,0:57:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我不确定能不能继续这样下去\N{\rEN}I'm not sure it works any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.85,0:58:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那 你想要什么\N{\rEN}So, what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.01,0:58:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我不确定自己想为你工作\N{\rEN}I'm not sure I want to work for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.68,0:58:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 你让我感到震惊\N{\rEN}Fine, you've got me over a barrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.56,0:58:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道这点 我知道这点 所以告诉我 你想要什么\N{\rEN}You know it, I know it, so tell me what you want
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.97,0:58:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-然后我们来谈谈  -你没搞明白\N{\rEN}-and let's get into it. -You don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.22,0:58:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我退出了 我不想成为这其中一份子\N{\rEN}I'm out. I don't want to be part of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.97,0:58:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 得了吧 别扯谈了\N{\rEN}Oh, come on. Fuck off!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.31,0:58:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"一本正经"小姐\N{\rEN}Little Miss Prim.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.10,0:58:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的\N{\rEN}You knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.81,0:58:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我是谁\N{\rEN}You know who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.64,0:58:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为情况已经变了 在细节方面\N{\rEN}I think it's changed. In the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.72,0:58:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你不需要去经历细节\N{\rEN}You don't walk over details.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.39,0:58:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,池子的底部深不可测\N{\rEN}I can't see the bottom of the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.89,0:58:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我...我...我不知道你是否还在乎什么\N{\rEN}I-- I-- I don't know if you care about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.47,0:58:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-这让我感到害怕  -噢 是的\N{\rEN}-And that scares me. -Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.81,0:58:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的语言 该死的表达 拜托 留下来\N{\rEN}Fucking words. Fucking words. Come on. Stay!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.64,0:58:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我总是能找到其他人的\N{\rEN}I could always find someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.81,0:59:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道你可以被人替代\N{\rEN}You know you're fungible.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.97,0:59:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-我无可替代  -噢 是的 你可以被替代\N{\rEN}-I am not fungible. -Oh, yes, you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.72,0:59:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈的可以被随意替代\N{\rEN}You're as fungible as fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.10,0:59:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEN}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.89,0:59:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那我替代我好了 来吧 试试\N{\rEN}Then funge me. Go ahead. Try.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.01,0:59:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞亚\N{\rEN}Rhea.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.72,0:59:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,今天 肯德尔·罗伊给参议院商务委员会\N{\rEN}Kendall Roy served self-satisfied hypocrites
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.06,0:59:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那些自欺欺人的伪君子们送上了一份现实派的健康部分\N{\rEN}on the senate commerce committee a healthy portion of reality pie
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.85,0:59:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他把他们打了个落花流水\N{\rEN}today when he delivered them a takedown for the ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.35,0:59:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,委员会里的民主党人对这家...\N{\rEN}Democrats on the committee had worked themselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.81,0:59:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-那...  -...历史悠久的公司\N{\rEN}-So... -...into a fit of phony outrage
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.76,0:59:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-产生了一阵虚假的愤怒  -瑞亚走了吗\N{\rEN}-over historic corporate... -Rhea's gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.68,0:59:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-但是他们做出了致命的错误估计  -是的\N{\rEN}-But they made a fatal miscalculation. -Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.01,0:59:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,她无法克服这种仇恨\N{\rEN}She can't hack the hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.39,0:59:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 那她可以滚蛋\N{\rEN}Well, she can fuck off
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.06,0:59:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,在一家他妈的电话公司\N{\rEN}and enjoy her lily-white, chicken-flesh conscience
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.97,0:59:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,享受她"纯洁无瑕" 的圣母心了\N{\rEN}working for a fucking phone company.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.93,0:59:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 是的 也许吧\N{\rEN}Yeah. Yeah, well, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.81,1:00:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 但是 你觉得这就完了吗\N{\rEN}Yeah, but do you think that's it?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.43,1:00:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,如果基拉不作证 而且我们牺牲掉比尔 你认为我们渡过难关了吗\N{\rEN}If Kira holds, and we kill Bill, do you think we're through?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.56,1:00:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,老实说吗\N{\rEN}Honestly?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.01,1:00:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 股东大会是道坎\N{\rEN}No. Not with the shareholders.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.06,1:00:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕肯德尔的这套话行不通\N{\rEN}I'm afraid this Kendall stuff won't play.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.89,1:00:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他们更像是...他妈的素食主义者\N{\rEN}They're a little more... fucking vegetarian.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.39,1:00:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,-不行吗  -不行\N{\rEN}-No? -No.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.35,1:00:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  是的\N{\rEN}Yes. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.01,1:00:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他像个战士一样 但我很受伤\N{\rEN}He came out like a fighter, but I'm hurt.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.22,1:00:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们很受伤\N{\rEN}We're hurt.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.10,1:00:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,比尔只是演习  他不会善罢甘休的\N{\rEN}And Bill's on maneuvers. He won't go quietly.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.22,1:00:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不  比尔不是答案\N{\rEN}No, no, no. Bill's not the answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.26,1:00:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要更高层的人\N{\rEN}We need something big.
